1. Scope, Importance, and Limitations of Marketing Research
âœ… Scope of Marketing Research:
Marketing research covers a wide range of areas, including:

Consumer Behavior Study â€“ Understanding needs, preferences, and buying habits.

Product Research â€“ Finding out the best product features, design, and packaging.

Price Research â€“ Analyzing what price consumers are willing to pay.

