ğŸ”¹ Example: During COVID-19, many pharma companies adjusted their supply chains to meet sudden demand for sanitizers and medicines.

âœï¸ Conclusion:
In todayâ€™s competitive business environment, supply chain management is not just a backend function â€” itâ€™s a strategic tool that impacts cost, customer satisfaction, growth, and survival. A well-managed supply chain can be the key to a companyâ€™s success.

