Gifts offered on the purchase of a product to attract customers.

ğŸ”¸ Example: â€œFree Lunch Box with School Bagâ€ or â€œFree Earphones with Mobile.â€

ğŸ”¹ B. Trade-Oriented Sales Promotion (Push Strategy)
