ğŸ”¸ Example: Comparing pricing and features of Pepsi vs Coca-Cola.

âœ… C. SWOT Analysis
A tool to study Strengths, Weaknesses, Opportunities, and Threats.

Internal	External
Strengths	Opportunities
Weaknesses	Threats
ğŸ”¸ Example: A strong brand name (strength), but rising raw material costs (threat)

âœ… D. Market Trend Analysis
