Psychological Pricing	â‚¹999 instead of â‚¹1000 to seem cheaper	Retail pricing
Discount Pricing	Temporary reductions to boost sales	Amazon Great Indian Sale
âœï¸ Conclusion:
Pricing is not just about assigning a number to a product â€” it is a strategic decision that affects sales, brand image, profits, and customer satisfaction. A well-thought-out pricing strategy can lead to increased market share, customer trust, and long-term business success.

